    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有三种方式可以描述 Unsound Love：<br>• 一个非线性、开放世界的密室逃脱体验——没有任何解释，一切都必须自己发现。<br>• 一个没有战斗的类 Souls 游戏。<br>• 将 Outer Wilds 与 Little Nightmares 融合在一起的诡异之作——被困在时间循环中，你必须探索、解开谜团，并在以恐怖为驱动的动作解谜过程中生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315700/extras/87b1a292388b66af2e582b581358fbb6.poster.avif?t=1772303886\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315700/extras/87b1a292388b66af2e582b581358fbb6.webm?t=1772303886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315700/extras/87b1a292388b66af2e582b581358fbb6.mp4?t=1772303886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从树林中的风声到怪物的咆哮，所有声音都由乐器演奏而成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315700/extras/a2743e7d4a0780139c514d7d2110835d.poster.avif?t=1772303886\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315700/extras/a2743e7d4a0780139c514d7d2110835d.webm?t=1772303886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315700/extras/a2743e7d4a0780139c514d7d2110835d.mp4?t=1772303886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们不被允许透露更多内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315700/extras/010d93d